Dairy Farmers Have Formed A Consortium Comprising Of Several Organizations, Seeking To Reduce The Plight That The Dairy Sector Undergoes. Farmers Are Complaining About The Cost Of Feeds For Their Animals Which Raises Costs Of Milk Production. Recently, The Dangerous Levels Of Aflatoxins Found In Maize, Is Also Causing Jitters In Farmers In Relation To Producing Quality Milk, Since Maize Contributes To The Animal Feeds.